o-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/coldplay_ralph_macchio-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/coldplay_ralph_macchio-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>周四，酷玩乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">(Coldplay</a> ) 首次现场表演了《空手道小子》，与 20 世纪 80 年代同名电影明星拉尔夫·马奇奥 (Ralph Macchio) 一起表演。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="624" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/coldplay-chris-martin-exclusive-nme-interview-moon-music-3798496"><b>酷玩乐队独家专访：“当事情显得极其积极时，通常是因为这是歌手最需要的”</b></a></li></ul><p> 10 月 31 日，随着<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-announce-expansion-of-music-of-the-spheres-tour-with-new-asia-dates-3795065">“Music Of The Spheres”世界巡演</a>澳大利亚和新西兰站的拉开序幕，“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/coldplay-moon-music-review-3798469">Moon Music</a> ”歌曲在乐队于墨尔本漫威体育场举行的第二场演出中首次亮相。</p><p>在开始这首歌之前，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-martin">克里斯·马丁</a>开玩笑说他快要失声了，并询问是否有人可以帮助他唱下一首歌曲。随后，在 80 年代<i>《空手道小子》</i>电影三部曲中饰演丹尼尔·拉鲁索的马基奥走上舞台，赢得了观众的热烈掌声。</p><p>当乐队开始这首歌时，马基奥似乎在跟着唱，但很快就发现他实际上是在模仿马丁自己预先录制的声音。社交媒体上的粉丝账户表明 Macchio 在那里拍摄了这首歌的视频。观看下面由粉丝拍摄的表演片段。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Coldplay - The Karate Kid - LIVE - Ft.拉尔夫·马基奥（Ralph Macchio）又名丹尼尔·拉鲁索（Daniel Larusso）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7mzju-CseaE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这是近几个月来，乐队第二次与 80 年代电影偶像同台演出，此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-honour-michael-eavis-and-michael-j-fox-at-glastonbury-2024-3770369">迈克尔·J·福克斯 (Michael J. Fox) 也曾在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 (Glastonbury) 上大获成功</a>。福克斯在安可期间演奏了三首歌曲，包括《Humankind》和《Fix You》。</p><h2> <strong>Coldplay 10 月 31 日在墨尔本漫威体育场的演出曲目：</strong> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="626" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“更高的力量”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="626" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“一生难忘的冒险”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="626" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;天堂&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="626" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559